@match Norgathu|norgathu
The kindom of Norgathu is a strong one. The king of Norgathu has an army of Giant Wolves under his control. The Great Dragons of Ice and Frost are seen frequently. There is rumored to be a tower there. People say that they spotted a great warrior riding upon a huge blue dragon.
@match tower|Tower
It is rumored that the five artifacts of Tredmar are stored there.
